{"tid":1300474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"康文署：擬修例管制曲藝表演","createTime":"2019-07-09T11:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T11:37:28.000Z","uid":212626,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9acd5e7618a445752ebaf6bd2607f2d061cd35b2","tid":1300474,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:23:32.000Z","msg":"屯門公園多年來被批遭「大媽」噪音滋擾，令區內居民怨聲載道，屯門區議會今日開會一致同意取消公園內的「自娛區」。<br />\n<br />\n康文署表示，已即時停止接受申請使用「自娛區」，而已申請使用的個案，據悉已排期至9月。<br />\n<br />\n署方又承認，現有規管公園曲藝表演的法例過時，將會修例並就不同的改善建議徵詢法律意見。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2187336/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2187336%2F&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7FEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=92ca174c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2187336/</a>"},{"pid":"97333a0ba04f93643630d5676a17e5d63eaa906a","tid":1300474,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:26:06.000Z","msg":"歡迎入內討論<br />\n<br />\n「長文慎入」勇武又好、和理非又好，自己香港自己救！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1299934/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1299934/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"68a0f52542bd66d61570e173d568d4fd396b7aa9","tid":1300474,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:28:03.000Z","msg":"擬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"decb6157f47ab01c57282647eab1fa6900b1bd35","tid":1300474,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68a0f52542bd66d61570e173d568d4fd396b7aa9","tid":1300474,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:28:03.000Z","msg":"擬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:28:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有希望"},{"pid":"196a65792d30e1add11296cb57986a8f329108a6","tid":1300474,"uid"